(68, 5, 11, 'Birthday Card Maker', 'app-68.jpg', 'Birthday Card Maker App lets you send unique and beautiful virtual birthday cards and your favorite Birthday Songs to friends, family and loved ones.\r\n Easily customize your design, share it via social media, sms, or print it. All you need is your smartphone  and 5 minutes max!\r\n\r\nBirthday Card Maker hands you hundreds of amazing templates, designed by pro graphic designer! Youâ€™ll be creating the best greeting cards or invitations EVER! \r\n\r\nCreate typography, edit texts and fonts, add a photo, or even change colors around easily and quickly! Now you are going to get the design you love and want, no more pretty complex tools.\r\n\r\nIf you are not feeling too creative just send birthday cards with quotes or some music \r\n\r\nBday is the most important day for anyone.\r\n\r\nWhether a boy or a girl, a lady or a man, baby or old one everyone waiting for this special day with hope of amazing gifts, party and funny happy birthday wishes.\r\n\r\nWith Birthday cards maker your birthday message is going to be remembered, for sure!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Birthday.Card.Maker&hl=en', 'https://www.greetingsisland.com/', 0, 1, 1, 0, '2020-04-09 15:44:27', '2020-04-09 15:44:27'),
