(104, 19, 7, 'AccuWeather: Weather forecast news & live radar', 'app-104.jpg', 'Accurate weather forecasts, real-time alerts, and severe weather warnings are available on-demand. Get today is weather forecast, storm alerts, live storm radar and much more!\r\n\r\nGet ready for the season with AccuWeather is weather alerts that are superior in their accuracy. Be prepared with the daily forecast or sudden severe changes in weather with live alerts and accurate weather forecasts. So whether thereâ€™s wind, rain, or even a hurricane - you can stay one step ahead with AccuWeather is weather radar.\r\nLocal forecasts, todayâ€™s temperature and more! Live weather stats give you real-time weather updates. From storm alerts to heavy rain, get all the severe weather warnings you need to protect you against any wind, rain or severe weather alert on the horizon.\r\n\r\nGo beyond today is weather forecast. From the daily forecast to snowstorm weather warnings, you control what type of information you get. Whether you want today is weather or today is temperature, AccuWeather is weather forecasting with a difference!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.accuweather.android&hl=en', '#', 0, 1, 1, 0, '2020-04-10 11:43:44', '2020-04-10 11:43:44'),
(105, 26, 8, 'Hill Climb Racing', 'app-105.png', 'One of the most addictive and entertaining physics based driving games ever made! And it is free!\r\n\r\nMeet Newton Bill, the young aspiring uphill racer. He is about to embark on a journey that takes him to where no ride has ever been before. From Ragnarok to a Nuclear Plant, all places are a racing track to Bill. With little respect to the laws of physics, Bill will not rest until he has conquered the highest hills up on the moon!\r\n\r\nFace the challenges of unique hill climbing environments with many different cars. Gain bonuses from daring tricks and collect coins to upgrade your car and reach even higher distances. Watch out though - Bill is stout neck is not what it used to be when he was a kid! And his good old gasoline crematorium will easily run out of fuel.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fingersoft.hillclimb&hl=en', 'https://fingersoft.com/contact/', 0, 1, 1, 0, '2020-04-10 12:58:34', '2020-04-10 12:58:34'),
