(108, 6, 8, 'Kotak - 811 & Mobile Banking', 'app-108.jpg', 'The Kotak Mobile Banking App, a best in class App, provides banking on the go, which is a must in todayâ€™s digital era.\r\n\r\nIf you are not an existing Kotak customer, you can open a Kotak Savings account or an 811 digital bank account by visiting your nearest branch.\r\n\r\nIf you are an existing Kotak customer, you can use the 100+ features of the app to Bank, Pay bills, Invest, Shop and access services.\r\nâ€¢ Bank on the go:\r\nManage all your financial transactions, send and receive money through NEFT, IMPS and RTGS & UPI, request for a cheque book and much more\r\nâ€¢ Shop at your fingertips:\r\nDive into KayMall and shop via Flipkart, book flights and hotel rooms via Goibibo and book train tickets via IRCTC and much more\r\nâ€¢ Pay your bills:\r\nPay your Mobile Recharge, DTH payments and other bills with the online BillPay feature. Also, use the AutoPay feature to remember your monthly bills and pay them automatically from your account. Never miss a deadline again\r\nâ€¢ Services:\r\nInstant completion on requesting for services such as updation of profile details, switching on/off of your Debit/Credit Card online\r\n', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.msf.kbank.mobile&hl=en', '#', 0, 1, 1, 0, '2020-04-10 13:07:57', '2020-04-10 13:07:57'),
(109, 7, 8, 'Zomato Restaurant Partner', 'app-109.png', 'Say hello to Zomato Restaurant Partner App! The redesigned app is much more than a name change and represents a massive overhaul in both performance & aesthetics.\r\n\r\nSWIFT ORDER MANAGEMENT\r\nA fresh design that focuses on maximising the visibility of order related information while ensuring a smooth and steady flow from Order Acceptance to Order Delivery.\r\n\r\nCONCISE APP JOURNEY\r\nImproved app interactions with minimal steps resulting in a simplified user experience.\r\n\r\nFEEDBACK FOR TIME LIMITS\r\nTimers in relevant steps like Acceptance, Preparation and Food-handover along with an enhanced feedback for delays.\r\n\r\nOTHER KEY FEATURES\r\n- Scheduling for leaves in advance to better manage occasional day-offs during festivals or personal work\r\n- Customer location share with self delivery riders via WhatsApp\r\n- Provision to mark entire menu category out of stock\r\n- Improved visibility of customer is order instructions.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.application.services.partner&hl=en', '#', 0, 1, 1, 0, '2020-04-10 13:10:42', '2020-04-10 13:10:42'),
